      </header>
    

    
    
    
    <div class="post-body" itemprop="articleBody">

      
      

      
        <p>由于Python是顶层高级语言，而C/C++属于底层语言。因此在运行的速度上Python是比不上C/C++。在此我分别用C++和Python写了两个相同的函数，然后分别来运行。</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>首先用C++写下如下内容，文件保存为pycall.cpp</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">extern &quot;C&quot; &#123; </span><br><span class="line">	void dosomething(int n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		for(int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) i *= 2;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在函数里面做一个for循环操作，循环的次数由参数n决定。<br>接着用gcc编译：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gcc -o libpycall.so -shared -fPIC pycall.cpp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>会生成一个libpycall.so文件。<br>接着在Python中调用C++，代码如下，文件命名为pythonCallC.py：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import ctypes</span><br><span class="line">import time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">start = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">ll = ctypes.cdll.LoadLibrary   </span><br><span class="line">lib = ll(&quot;./libpycall.so&quot;) </span><br><span class="line">lib.dosomething(100000) </span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;**call by c++**&quot;) </span><br><span class="line">print(time.time() - start)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>其中，导入time库来计时，里面主要做的事情就是循环10万次。<br>同样在另外一个Python文件中写下如下代码，文件命名为pythonSelf.py：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def dosomething(n):</span><br><span class="line">	for i in range(n):</span><br><span class="line">		i *= 2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">start = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">dosomething(100000)</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;**call by python**&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">print(time.time() - start)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>最后在terminal中运行这两个Python文件，结果如下：</p>
<p><img src="http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79ly1g5fxtplb75j30m606w3zr.jpg" alt="这里写图片描述"></p>
<p>可以看出，在Python中调用C++的执行速度要快于Python中直接执行的速度。特别是要实现的功能越复杂，差距越大。如果执行很简单的操作的话，就不好体现出C++的执行速度的优势。比如，可以看出，当只循环1000次的时候，Python还是比C++快很多的。</p>
<p><img src="http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79ly1g5fxthnirlj30m607gq4s.jpg" alt="这里写图片描述"></p>

      
